# Long-Term Vision

After the VTM plugin is complete, additional systems can be added without modifying the Core Engine.

Planned plugins include:

* Call of Cthulhu 7e
* Dungeons & Dragons 5e
* Pathfinder 2e
* Lancer
* Generic RPG System

The long-term objective is for StoryForge to become a flexible platform capable of managing campaigns for any tabletop RPG through a shared, game-agnostic engine.
